                    <h1>Hanif Abdurraqib is building new worlds with a concert series</h1>

                      <h2 class="deck">The celebrated cultural critic discusses his work organizing the 2022 spring season of Music at BAM.</h2>


                    <div class="credits">
                        <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/raphael-helfand">Raphael Helfand</a></span>
  </div>


<div class="posted">
  <div>
    March 24, 2022
  </div>
</div>

                    </div>

